{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=b07cfd08a9b5ed68d1bc9d9d94d73528&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fa5c27d1ed21b0ef4357c3372d5c451da81cb3e01.jpg","summary":"包头职业技术学院坐落于享有“塞外明珠”“草原钢城”美誉的全国首批文明城市——包头，是国家百所示范性高等职业院校之一。学院前身是创建于1956年的国家级重点中等专业学校——包头机械工业学校。1998年成为全国最早独立设置的14所公办职业技术院校之一，并更名为包头职业技术学院。2016年8月，入选第二批国家现代学徒制试点单位。截至2017年3月，学校有建华、呼得木林、北重集团3个校区，占地面积73.36万平方米，建筑面积35.19万平方米，固定资产总值6.26亿元，其中教学仪器设备总值超过1.31亿元；有11个教学系部，开设51个专业，试办高职本科专业4个；有专任教师496人，全日制在校生10462人，成人教育在校生142人。","tags":["理工类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1956","所在地区":"包头市青山区呼得木林大街12号","院校隶属":"内蒙古自治区教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=31d79ff6a3aeb32bdc9506bcb5affb94&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3646814891%2C767706062%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=3ed6626347585be79cab418dcd75dd09&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3377349520%2C3796752454%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=9f383dca7dec8cb368da6b5fa2cf3a4c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3591446776%2C844852728%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=521fcb922b37755e3e568b5a64ab19a0&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3650519121%2C4013377995%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=4d29fd8c23a7f9503b580f854bca5252&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3541493407%2C3892982632%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg